    "updated_at": "2014-11-07T03:18:13Z",
    "body": "I tried with Scroll Lock instead of Numlock and the Alt key unhide works fine with it on.\n\nI tried with Caps Lock instead of Num Lock and it behaves just like when Num Lock is on. The menu will not unhide when the Alt key is pressed.\n\nI'm currently looking at:\n\natom\\browser\\native_window_views.cc\n\nSpecifically at the HandleKeyboardEvent function. I can see exactly where it's not passing through the if conditions. Perhaps we need a condition in there to ignore if Num Lock and Caps Lock are pressed so that it can pass through.\n"
